            <li><strong>Education:</strong> Through our barista school, we aim to spread knowledge and passion for coffee, nurturing the next generation of coffee artisans.</li>
        </ul>
    
        <p>Whether you're a casual coffee lover or an aspiring barista, <strong>Second Cup</strong> is the place for you. Come by and let us share our passion for coffee with you!</p>
